 2x fitness bread

Advantages of the Mestemacher premium wholemeal bread basket

 The 2 x 5 different types of fitness bread, pure wholemeal bread, sun seed bread, pumpernickel and linseed bread are hygienically packaged.
 The 5 different types of wholemeal bread are ideal for testing to taste your favorite type.


 Depending on your personal mood and the time of day, you can choose a different bread for breakfast, after exercise, during the lunch break or for dinner.


 The individually wrapped discs are well suited for people who work and therefore don't want to spend much time shopping.


 The bread in the hygienic portion packs can be enjoyed unopened for up to 12 months thanks to natural pasteurisation.


 Single households that consume smaller amounts of bread do not have to worry about the bread becoming moldy.


 Wholemeal bread is important for a healthy high-fiber diet.


 Freshly ground rye is used to make the bread. As a result, the (high) content of vitamins and minerals is well preserved. , MESTEMACHER GmbH has provided the above information.
